data.description: This 3.15-acre single-story haven in The Oaklands offers a slice of the spectacular Texas Hill Country lifestyle. The custom estate is meticulously built, featuring exquisite finishes and craftsmanship. Upon entry, a well-appointed study with extensive custom-built ins welcomes you. The chef's kitchen is outfitted with professional-grade stainless steel appliances and a granite island with counter seating and a copper farmhouse sink. The spacious master retreat boasts a sun-filled bathroom with custom cabinetry, a walk-in shower, and an oversized closet. Guest bedrooms are generous, each with large closets. Outdoors, enjoy the serenity of a large covered patio, pool, and spa amid pristine landscaping that ensures privacy. The forest of trees behind your property provides a stunning backdrop, creating a true park-like setting. The oversized side-entry three-car garage includes custom built-ins, and steps lead up to a temperature-controlled space ideal for additional storage, a workout room, or an extra game room, offering endless possibilities.
